headline: Eversource Energy Schedules Second Quarter Earnings Call
summary: HARTFORD, Conn. & BOSTON, July 09, 2025--Eversource Energy will host an earnings conference call with financial analysts on Friday, August 1, 2025, at 9 a.m. Eastern Time, to discuss the company’s financial performance and other business updates through the second quarter of 2025.
